How do I become a seller here?

We are not a community and don't offer any services to have sellers or buyers

Wowlfg now is just a platform for people to find people to help them in game either free (LFG) or in exchange for gold as long as it is within Blizz ToS (LFB). Basically, people list an offer and other people sign up to the offer and the person who posted the offer can pick them and independently pay them within the Blizz ToS

So, tldr, we don't really have sellers as we don't sell anything 

If you want to know how to use WoWLFG, check https://wowlfg.com/guides
